        <body>
            <div xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"><head><anchor xml:id="xmlid__heading_h_640cvs634qjl"/><hi rend="baseline">İSTM.ŞSC.14.d. 352/ 6a-1_</hi><ref target="http://document__35"><hi rend="baseline underline color(1155cc)">GrocerIST id_35</hi></ref></head><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi>Mahrūse-i Galata tevābi‘nden İstinye nāhiyesine tābi‘ kasaba-i Yeniköyde vāki‘</hi><hi style="font-size:8.5pt" xml:space="preserve">  </hi><hi xml:space="preserve">Kürkçü mahallesinde mütemekkin iken bundan akdem hālik olan bakkāl Simal veled-i Nikolanın verāseti zevcesi Kasandıra bt. Kakod ve sulbiye kebīre kızı </hi><hi rend="background(yellow)">….</hi><hi xml:space="preserve">Aragorya ve sulbī sagīr oğlu </hi><hi rend="background(yellow)">…</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> münhasıra olduğu şer’an zāhir oldukdan sonra sagīr mesfūr </hi><hi rend="background(yellow)">..</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> ile </hi><hi rend="background(yellow)">…</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> tesviye-i emrlerine  kıbel-i şer‘-i şerīf-i vasī nasb olunan Dimitri veled-i Yani ve mesfūre Kasandıra taleb ve iltimāslarıyla tahrīr olunan tereke-i hālik mesfūrdur ki ber vech-i ātī zikr olunur. 8 rebiülevvel 1173</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold">Tencere:</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> 2 / 360</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold">Sini:</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> 400</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold">Güğüm:</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> 360</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold">İhram :</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> 3 / 300</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold">Beledī yasdık:</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> 4 / 400</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold">Beledī yasdık döşek:</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> 360</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold">Taba, tencere (6):</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> 360</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold" xml:space="preserve">Kurşun mum </hi><hi rend="bold background(yellow)">…</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> 45</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold">Köhne nāfe kürk:</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> 240</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold">Kazgan:</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> 500</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold">Kebe:</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> 2 / 360</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold">Yorgan:</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> 480</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold">Çuka cübbe:</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> 300</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold background(yellow)" xml:space="preserve">…: </hi><hi>180</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold">Köhne kuşak ve kalpak:</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> 180</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold">Çārşeb:</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> 120</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold">Köhne entari:</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> 2 / 360</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold">Dizlik ve kaliçe:</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> 180</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold">Kazgan:</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> 1440</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold">Laza:</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> 3 / 1200</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold">Varil:</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> 8 / 480</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold">Varil:</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> 120</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold">Kutu çift:</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> 5 / 600</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold">Hasır:</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> 120</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi>Hālik mesfūrun kasaba-i Yeniköyde bağlar hilālinde vāki’ kürumi mülk-ü bağ 2 kıt’a ber vech-i tahmin: 36000</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi>Hālik mesfūrun kasaba-i mezkūrede vāki‘ mülk-ü menzil kıymeti ber vech-i tahmīn zikr olunur: 48000</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi>Bağların mahsūlunden hāsıl olan meblağ: 24000</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi>Kezālik mülk-ü mesfūrun kasaba-i mezkūrede vāki’ bakkāl dükkānında olan eşyā vesāir ālāt-ı lāzıme kıymeti : 48000</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi>Kürekçi Karlo veled-i Kostadan makbūz: 60000</hi></p></div>
